
Git Clone Error---fatal: Out of memory, malloc failed 
=======================================================

Add swap memory in server OR increase RAM of Server

# fallocate -l 4G /swapfile
# chmod 600 /swapfile
# mkswap /swapfile
# swapon /swapfile

Make these changes permanent by adding to /etc/fstab:

# vi /etc/fstab
...
/swapfile   none    swap    sw    0   0
#


Recommend adding to /etc/sysctl.conf:

# vi /etc/sysctl.conf
...
vm.swappiness=10
vm.vfs_cache_pressure = 50
#
